  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK904">
<l>maṉaiyāḷai yañcu maṟumaiyilāḷaṉ</l>
<l>viṉaiyāṇmai vīṟeyta liṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The undertaking of one, who fears his wife and is therefore destitute of (bliss), will never be applauded.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
